          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " and click on the “Login” button on the top right. You will be asked to input your email address. After doing so, you will receive an email with a link that allows you to log in. You no longer need a password to log in to your account.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
